name: Gift voucher (choose from $50 to $250)
description: Not sure what to get? Not sure which photography session they might like? Get them a gift voucher and they can put the money towards the session of their choice! :)

name: $200 Photography session voucher
description:
This voucher entitles the bearer to a photographic session with Nikki Yetman to the value of $200.00 including:-

*My time to photograph your session in my studio or local outdoor location
* My many hours time to professionally edit your images
* 10 high resolution images supplied in colour with copies in black & white and sepia on CD
* Storyboard collage
* Facebook sneak peak by 10pm on the day of your shoot
* Your CD of images posted within 2 weeks of your session

Valid for 6 months from date of issue, not redeemable for cash.

name: $495 Maternity & Newborn Photography Package
description:
Not sure what to get her? What about some beautiful photographs to capture this incredible "miracle of life" journey and her precious newborn baby? The gift that keeps on giving long after this time is over - images she can treasure forever. Ideal as a baby shower gift, this package includes:

* Studio/outdoor maternity shoot
* 15 x maternity photographs
* Studio newborn shoot
* 15 x newborn photographs
* Before bub and after bump comparison image
* Bonus storyboard maternity collage
* Bonus storyboard newborn collage
* All images supplied in high resolution format in colour with copies in black & white and sepia on CD
* BONUS birth announcement digital file included on newborn cd provided newborn shoot is completed before the little one is 12 days old.
* My many hours time to professionally edit all images.
